{"type": "article", "id": 10295, "title": "Tokujin Yoshioka “V” 表", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-02T07:15:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052354403vpi8c4VsEfbyNag.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是日本设计师 Tokujin Yoshioka 为 ISSEY MIYAKE 推出的一款全新的 “V” 表，其最大的特色在于表带利用不锈钢的挤出成型技术打造出不同的 V 型凹槽，从而从不同的角度都可以反射出光芒，看上去十分美丽。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354379DS0vEYfhNqxMT5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235438kmhDBunp8ZWHSAV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.47291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235438VvCDhy3Yqab475Ug.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.23333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235439PrsJ8DdyB9jXSomT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354392mW7ky6wfO9vLjT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68229167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}